content.description: Starts with shallow fingers, small hands, side pulls, and toe boxes for first 20 feet to ledge. Up ledge through wider stuff with some good jamming, stemming, and a short offwidth finish.Â
content.protection: Doubles through #2, single #3, double # 4. May supplement some with hexes. Two bolt anchor with chains at top.
content.location: Left of In and Out start about 80 feet. You'll see a finger crack separated by larger crack above ledge.

content.description: Start on In&Out, after the first 15 ft stay right on flared fingers up thru a bulge. Crux is 5.10double-D afterwards probably only 5.9 but still a bit dirty-- will return and brush off more of the lichen soon. The rock itself is excellent and takes good pro the whole way.
content.protection: a f#4 or two for the start of In&Out then double fingers with one #.75 and #1, and bust couple nuts!

content.description: In & Out, will go your hands, fists, arms, even whole body on this one. Consistent fun on three sections divided between two nice rests/ledges. Great rock although sandy, though will get cleaner on more ascents. Great pro, fun, varied movement. Rap from 2 glue-in bolts.
content.protection: BD sizes, one #1, three #3's, three #4's, two #5's. Include a couple longer runners.
content.location: Crack in center of wall, starts hands then through obvious short chimney to offwidth finish.

content.description: Clean, bouldery start past single bolt for crux start, then continue on easier crack through fun collection of jams and crimps.
content.protection: One bolt, doubles in tips to 0.5, singles .75 through 2 bd, nuts.
content.location: On far left side of wall, on clean face below crack. Look for single bolt on clean rock at start.

content.description: Fun climb, from most angles it just looks like a chimney but there is a nice crack in the back that takes great gear. It look's harder than it is and the moves are interesting. The spice is right at the top.
content.protection: Doubles in fingers and hands, a few small cams, and two fours.
content.location: The right side of the wall.

content.description: 70-90 foot wall with a few routes, close to main trail for for fun with the partner of your choice.
